name: The Twins
description: [ENG] - the twins is a digitalized linocut that portrays the combination of feelings that does away with any sanity in the urban environment, anxiety and loneliness. without the connection with nature, often without connections with people, the urban environment deteriorates our relationships and rushes us so voraciously that it consumes our energy and makes us feel incapable, weak and replaceable in the midst of production processes, in any area.-[PT/BR] v√£o no tradutor por favor.
